+ * Device tree based initialization code for reserved memory.
+ *
+ * Copyright (c) 2013, The Linux Foundation. All Rights Reserved.
+ * Copyright (c) 2013,2014 Samsung Electronics Co., Ltd.
+ *		http://www.samsung.com
